## 1Ô∏è‚É£ Problem Statement & Solution

### Problem Statement
> Traditional campus grievance systems are slow, inefficient, and frustrating for students. Issues get lost, misrouted, or take weeks to resolve without any transparency.

**Key Problems:**
- üìù Manual categorization leads to errors and delays
- ‚è∞ No SLA tracking or accountability
- üîÑ Complaints often sent to wrong departments
- üìä No data-driven insights for campus administration
- üò§ Students have no visibility into resolution progress
- üó£Ô∏è Fear of retaliation prevents anonymous reporting

### Our Solution: CampusAI
> An AI-powered grievance management system that uses Google Gemini to instantly classify, route, and track campus issues with full transparency.

**How It Works:**
1. Student describes issue in natural language (text or voice)
2. Gemini AI instantly analyzes and classifies the complaint
3. Auto-routes to the correct department with urgency level
4. Real-time tracking with SLA countdown
5. AI chatbot for instant FAQs and status updates

