| **Google Fonts** | Typography | Inter font family for modern, clean UI across all pages |
| **Google Material Design** | Design System | Color palette, spacing, component design principles |

### Gemini API Features Used

| Feature | Application |
|---------|-------------|
| **Text Classification** | Categorize grievances into departments |
| **Sentiment Analysis** | Detect student emotions (frustrated, angry, concerned) |
| **Entity Extraction** | Pull out locations, equipment names, timestamps |
| **Urgency Scoring** | AI-assigned priority (critical/high/medium/low) |
| **Response Generation** | Auto-generate acknowledgements and updates |
| **Image Understanding** | Detect issues from photos (Gemini Vision) |
| **Multi-modal Input** | Process both text and images together |

### Gemini Models Used

| Model | Use Case |
|-------|----------|
| `gemini-1.5-flash` | Fast classification & chat responses |
| `gemini-1.5-flash` (Vision) | Image analysis for uploaded photos |

### Detailed Integration

**1. Grievance Classification Prompt:**
```
Analyze this campus grievance and provide:
- Category (hostel/academic/it/canteen/transport/security)
- Urgency (critical/high/medium/low) with score
- Department to route to
- Sentiment analysis (frustrated/angry/concerned/neutral)
- Keywords extraction
- Suggested action for admin
- Confidence score
```

**2. Image Analysis Prompt:**
```
Analyze this image and identify infrastructure/maintenance issues:
- Description of visible problems
- Suggested category
- Urgency level
- List of detected issues
- Safety hazard assessment
```

**3. Student Response Generation:**
```
Generate a friendly acknowledgement message including:
- Ticket ID reference
- Expected resolution time
- Department assigned
- What to expect next
```

